---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/marketing/SectionHeader.astro";
import StatCard from "../components/marketing/StatCard.astro";

const icons = {
  grid: '<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" /><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" /><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" /><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" /></svg>',
  clock: '<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" /></svg>',
  pulse: '<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2" /></svg>',
  dollar: '<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23" /><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" /></svg>',
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Crisis | Sparcle — Why Modern Work Is Broken"
  description="Research-backed data on workplace fragmentation: 473 SaaS apps per enterprise, 47-second attention spans, $450B annual productivity loss. The hidden crisis driving Sparcle."
  canonical="https://sparcle.app/crisis"
>
  <section id="crisis" class="section-problem section-problem--page">
    <div class="container">
      <SectionHeader
        label="The Hidden Crisis"
        heading="Modern Work Is Broken — And Cloud AI Makes It Worse"
        intro="Dr. Gloria Mark's research at UC Irvine revealed a startling truth: attention spans collapsed from 2.5 minutes to 47 seconds in two decades. Microsoft's Work Trend Index confirms 48% of employees describe work as 'chaotic.' This isn't anecdotal — it's systemic."
      />

      <div class="problem-stats-grid">
        <StatCard
          title="473"
          text="SaaS apps per enterprise"
          impact="Each demanding credentials, attention, cognitive overhead"
          icon={icons.grid}
          titleSize="2.5rem"
        />
        <StatCard
          title="28%"
          text="Of workweek on email"
          impact="Only 39% spent on actual role-specific work (McKinsey)"
          icon={icons.clock}
          titleSize="2.5rem"
        />
        <StatCard
          title="47s"
          text="Average attention span"
          impact="Down from 2.5 minutes — 'attention residue' reduces capacity"
          icon={icons.pulse}
          titleSize="2.5rem"
        />
        <StatCard
          title="$450B"
          text="Annual U.S. productivity loss"
          impact="The true cost of workplace fragmentation (Asana Anatomy of Work)"
          icon={icons.dollar}
          titleSize="2.5rem"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="problem-conclusion">
        <p>
          <strong>Existing solutions fall short.</strong> They lock you into their ecosystem.
          It's by design — that's their core business model. Every major AI assistant sends your
          employees' data and documents to cloud infrastructure outside your control. We don't
          believe in vendor lock-in.
        </p>
        <p>
          The regulated economy — healthcare ($4.3T), financial services ($4.6T), defense ($886B),
          legal ($350B) — cannot adopt cloud-only AI. Not because they don't want to. Because their
          compliance frameworks, regulations, and fiduciary duties to customers won't allow it.
          That's the market existing AI vendors are ignoring. It's the market we're building for.
        </p>

        <h3 class="cmp-heading">Bolt vs. Copilot 365 &amp; Gemini Workspace</h3>
        <p class="cmp-subtext">Microsoft Copilot 365 is a $30/seat add-on charged <em>on top of</em> existing M365 licenses ($12–22/seat), totaling $42–52/seat — and requires your data to route through Microsoft's Azure OpenAI cloud. Gemini Workspace similarly processes your documents externally.</p>

        <style>
          .cmp-wrap { overflow-x: auto; margin: 0 0 3rem; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
          .cmp { width: 100%; min-width: 580px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 1rem; }
          .cmp colgroup col:first-child { width: 55%; }
          .cmp colgroup col:not(:first-child) { width: 22.5%; }
          .cmp thead tr { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-strong, rgba(255,255,255,0.12)); }
          .cmp th { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9375rem; }
          .cmp th:first-child { text-align: left; }
          .cmp th:not(:first-child) { text-align: center; }
          .cmp tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle, rgba(255,255,255,0.06)); transition: background 0.15s; }
          .cmp tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
          .cmp tbody tr:hover { background: var(--bg-surface-glass); }
          .cmp td { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; vertical-align: middle; }
          .cmp td:first-child { text-align: left; color: var(--text-body); }
          .cmp td:not(:first-child) { text-align: center; }
          .cmp-heading { margin: 2.5rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
          .cmp-subtext { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
          .cmp-yes { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-success-bg); color: var(--color-success); }
          .cmp-no { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-danger-bg); color: var(--color-danger); }
          .cmp-partial { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-warning-bg); color: var(--color-warning); }
          .cmp-note { display: block; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.25rem; font-weight: 400; }
          .cmp-hero-val { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-success); }
          .cmp-th-ours { color: var(--brand-primary, #818cf8); }
          .cmp-section-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0.25rem; }
        </style>

        <div class="cmp-wrap">
          <table class="cmp">
            <colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th></th>
                <th class="cmp-th-ours">Bolt</th>
                <th>Copilot 365 · Gemini</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Self-hosted / air-gapped deployment</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Bring Your Own LLM — switch anytime</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><span class="cmp-note">Vendor-locked model</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Works with any IdP — 365, Workspace, Zoho, Okta&hellip;</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><span class="cmp-note">Own ecosystem only</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>IP &amp; PII protected from AI model</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Data stays completely on-prem</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>HIPAA / ITAR / SOX deployable</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Price per seat / month</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-hero-val">$10</span></td>
                <td><strong>$42–52</strong><span class="cmp-note">$30 Copilot add-on + M365 base</span></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin:2.5rem 0 0.5rem;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;">Aeira vs. Glean</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--text-muted,#6b7280);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Glean is the leading enterprise search tool. It's cloud-hosted, SaaS-only, and routes all document indexing through Glean's infrastructure. Aeira offers equivalent search capability — with full data sovereignty.</p>

        <div class="cmp-wrap">
          <table class="cmp">
            <colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th></th>
                <th class="cmp-th-ours">Aeira</th>
                <th>Glean</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Self-hosted / on-prem deployment</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><span class="cmp-note">SaaS only</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>4-level ACL filtering — org / group / role / user</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-partial"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="cmp-note">Partial</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Documents indexed inside your perimeter</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Bring Your Own LLM for AI answers</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-yes"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span></td>
                <td><span class="cmp-no"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Price per seat / month</td>
                <td><span class="cmp-hero-val">Bundled</span><span class="cmp-note">Included with Bolt</span></td>
                <td><strong>~$20–40</strong></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="section-cta-row">
          <a href="/research.html" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z" />
              <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z" />
            </svg>
            View Research &amp; Whitepaper
          </a>
          <a href="/solution" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            See Our Solution
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
